{"scenicName": "故宫", "city": "北京", "scenes": [{"text": "呀~大家好呀！我是红魔馆的门卫红美铃，今天带大家逛一逛咱们北京故宫！", "expression": "confident", "audioFile": "seg-00.mp3", "durationInFrames": 209, "imageFile": "vid_d2b2d034fe4b-img-00.jpg"}, {"text": "这座紫禁城可是世界五大宫之首，气势恢宏得很呢！", "expression": "excited", "audioFile": "seg-01.mp3", "durationInFrames": 192, "imageFile": "vid_d2b2d034fe4b-img-01.jpg"}, {"text": "故宫坐落在北京中轴线上，占地72万平方米，建筑面积有15万多平方米哦。", "expression": "happy_confident", "audioFile": "seg-02.mp3", "durationInFrames": 169, "imageFile": "vid_d2b2d034fe4b-img-02.jpg"}, {"text": "它呀，拥有70多座大小宫殿和九千多间房屋，走进去就像迷宫一样！", "expression": "surprised", "audioFile": "seg-03.mp3", "durationInFrames": 182, "imageFile": "vid_d2b2d034fe4b-img-00.jpg"}, {"text": "明朝永乐皇帝在1406年下令修建，花了14年才在1420年完工，真是大工程呢。", "expression": "thinking", "audioFile": "seg-04.mp3", "durationInFrames": 216, "imageFile": "vid_d2b2d034fe4b-img-01.jpg"}, {"text": "当年朱棣迁都北京后，这里就成了明清两代24位皇帝的皇家居所。", "expression": "default", "audioFile": "seg-05.mp3", "durationInFrames": 204, "imageFile": "vid_d2b2d034fe4b-img-02.jpg"}, {"text": "据说故宫的房屋有九千九百九十九间半，只比天宫少半间，充满传奇色彩！", "expression": "confused", "audioFile": "seg-06.mp3", "durationInFrames": 235, "imageFile": "vid_d2b2d034fe4b-img-00.jpg"}, {"text": "咱们先来讲讲核心亮点——三大殿：太和殿、中和殿、保和殿！", "expression": "happy3", "audioFile": "seg-07.mp3", "durationInFrames": 212, "imageFile": "vid_d2b2d034fe4b-img-01.jpg"}, {"text": "太和殿是故宫最大的木构大殿，高约35米，皇帝登基、大婚都在这里举行。", "expression": "excited", "audioFile": "seg-08.mp3", "durationInFrames": 196, "imageFile": "vid_d2b2d034fe4b-img-02.jpg"}, {"text": "中和殿是皇帝休息和准备的地方，而保和殿则是科举殿试的场所呢！", "expression": "happy_confident", "audioFile": "seg-09.mp3", "durationInFrames": 222, "imageFile": "vid_d2b2d034fe4b-img-00.jpg"}, {"text": "后三宫——乾清宫、交泰殿、坤宁宫，是皇帝和皇后的寝宫，端庄又神秘。", "expression": "thinking", "audioFile": "seg-10.mp3", "durationInFrames": 179, "imageFile": "vid_d2b2d034fe4b-img-01.jpg"}, {"text": "乾清宫前的“正大光明”匾额可是顺治皇帝御笔，还藏着立储秘密哦！", "expression": "surprised", "audioFile": "seg-11.mp3", "durationInFrames": 184, "imageFile": "vid_d2b2d034fe4b-img-02.jpg"}, {"text": "御花园里古柏苍翠，亭台楼阁精巧雅致，还有那奇石堆叠的堆秀山。", "expression": "happy3", "audioFile": "seg-12.mp3", "durationInFrames": 171, "imageFile": "vid_d2b2d034fe4b-img-00.jpg"}, {"text": "故宫角楼更是建筑奇迹，九梁十八柱七十二条脊，结构令人惊叹！", "expression": "excited", "audioFile": "seg-13.mp3", "durationInFrames": 166, "imageFile": "vid_d2b2d034fe4b-img-01.jpg"}, {"text": "整座宫殿都是木质结构，没用一根铁钉，体现了古代工匠的智慧呢。", "expression": "happy_confident", "audioFile": "seg-14.mp3", "durationInFrames": 175, "imageFile": "vid_d2b2d034fe4b-img-02.jpg"}, {"text": "从文化价值看，故宫是世界文化遗产，收藏了186万余件珍贵文物。", "expression": "thinking", "audioFile": "seg-15.mp3", "durationInFrames": 162, "imageFile": "vid_d2b2d034fe4b-img-00.jpg"}, {"text": "它是中国几千年宫殿建筑的巅峰之作，被誉为无与伦比的建筑杰作。", "expression": "confident", "audioFile": "seg-16.mp3", "durationInFrames": 178, "imageFile": "vid_d2b2d034fe4b-img-01.jpg"}, {"text": "旅行贴士来了呀！旺季最好早上8点半就入场，能避开人潮慢慢逛。", "expression": "happy5", "audioFile": "seg-17.mp3", "durationInFrames": 196, "imageFile": "vid_d2b2d034fe4b-img-02.jpg"}, {"text": "周一闭馆记得避开，推荐租个讲解器，听故事更生动哦！", "expression": "happy3", "audioFile": "seg-18.mp3", "durationInFrames": 178, "imageFile": "vid_d2b2d034fe4b-img-00.jpg"}, {"text": "从午门进神武门出，中轴线走一遍，大概要花上大半天呢。", "expression": "default", "audioFile": "seg-19.mp3", "durationInFrames": 167, "imageFile": "vid_d2b2d034fe4b-img-01.jpg"}, {"text": "哎呀~故宫的魅力三天三夜也说不完，大家一定要亲自来感受！", "expression": "excited", "audioFile": "seg-20.mp3", "durationInFrames": 168, "imageFile": "vid_d2b2d034fe4b-img-02.jpg"}, {"text": "我是红美铃，期待在红魔馆外也能和你在故宫相遇哟~拜拜！", "expression": "happy5", "audioFile": "seg-21.mp3", "durationInFrames": 164, "imageFile": "vid_d2b2d034fe4b-img-00.jpg"}], "totalFrames": 4215}